  "detailed_description": "Soul of Roses is a 2D rogue light action game.<br>Absorb the abilities of your enemies, fight, die, revive, and repeat as you progress through the story.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2191770/extras/3e9b45a6ea7ecc17cda1bfdfb46592f8.poster.avif?t=1738934819\" width=620 height=348 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2191770/extras/3e9b45a6ea7ecc17cda1bfdfb46592f8.webm?t=1738934819\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2191770/extras/3e9b45a6ea7ecc17cda1bfdfb46592f8.mp4?t=1738934819\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >What is Gregory House?</h2>It is a hotel in another dimension where souls who have not been satisfied in the real world arrive.<br>The inhabitants of this world all release their desires and live their lives as they please.<br>At Gregory House, “strength of thought” is everything.<br>Even if your body perishes, you can reject death as long as your heart is not broken.<br>It is the same for the other residents.<br>Therefore, it is safe to beat up the residents.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2191770/extras/16d5d1f9907d6c037d4a6911e21102d7.avif?t=1738934819\" width=620 height=292 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >The Battle to Regain Memory.</h2>Gregory House is in trouble when it is attacked by runaway zombies.<br>You awoke as one of the zombies, unable to remember even your own name.<br>Gregory, the caretaker of Gregory House, offers you a contract.<br>If you will restore peace to Gregory House, I will help you regain your memory.<br>Your battle to restore peace to Gregory House and to regain your own memories begins.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2191770/extras/8aecc8f4ecab3df1efabf3ba675f3707.poster.avif?t=1738934819\" width=620 height=166 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2191770/extras/8aecc8f4ecab3df1efabf3ba675f3707.webm?t=1738934819\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2191770/extras/8aecc8f4ecab3df1efabf3ba675f3707.mp4?t=1738934819\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Transform with the Soul Taker! </h2>Take the souls of your enemies with the Soul Taker, a mysterious device embedded in your hand.<br>By eating the souls you take, you can transform into a soul style that reflects your opponent's abilities!<br>There are as many souls as there are enemies, so you are sure to find the perfect soul style for you.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2191770/extras/671cad35b7f32b26c2fd0750d260ec39.poster.avif?t=1738934819\" width=620 height=266 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2191770/extras/671cad35b7f32b26c2fd0750d260ec39.webm?t=1738934819\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2191770/extras/671cad35b7f32b26c2fd0750d260ec39.mp4?t=1738934819\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Diverse battle styles!</h2>Find your own way of fighting by combining “Memory” and “Soul Style” to strengthen yourself!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2191770/extras/678cd7afd780c2aad92164c52fb0b49f.poster.avif?t=1738934819\" width=620 height=216 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2191770/extras/678cd7afd780c2aad92164c52fb0b49f.webm?t=1738934819\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2191770/extras/678cd7afd780c2aad92164c52fb0b49f.mp4?t=1738934819\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >LOCAL CO-OP! </h2>Play with a friend in the two-player co-op mode!<br>Fight your enemies together in local co-op or online using the Steam's Remote Play Together feature.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2191770/extras/00213bab53cb2d46637ca511e799d340.poster.avif?t=1738934819\" width=620 height=236 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2191770/extras/00213bab53cb2d46637ca511e799d340.webm?t=1738934819\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2191770/extras/00213bab53cb2d46637ca511e799d340.mp4?t=1738934819\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Lots of fun inhabitants! </h2>Many colorful, cute, and slightly funny inhabitants appear!<br>Have fun chatting with them and eating their souls.",
